{"tid":362243,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見]日本東北四寺制霸","createTime":"2017-08-16T19:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T06:21:13.000Z","uid":8203,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98b515611ae1393f6bc7db22d6808678af1fd135","tid":362243,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T19:15:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟都有去過幾次日本<br />\n不過東北真係第一次 希望各位大大比D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見D景點真係好疏所以真係驚驚<br />\n加上日子唔多 真係好無奈<br />\n<br />\nday1:三點到成田 直接換pass食埋個飯上青森<br />\n<br />\nday2:朝早如果有漁市場就逛下 然後a factory九半開門即入 有時間去埋個夢魔展覽館 <br />\n中午五能線睇青池 (仲有咩地方值得去唔知求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n五能線係咪要揀特別車所以得番13:51個班揀？<br />\n去到十二湖已經五點就快日落仲入唔入到青池<br />\n定應該放棄呢架車揀其他車？<br />\n<br />\n夜晚入秋田<br />\n<br />\nday3:秋田內陸線 去完入平泉<br />\n<br />\nday4:平泉中尊寺+毛越寺 之後去仙台食野 宿秋保溫泉<br />\n<br />\nday5:朝早挑戰立石寺 下午去松島瑞巖寺 睇埋松島日落 夜晚落東京<br />\n<br />\nday6:東京鳩遊 然後就羽田凌晨機返香港<br />\n<br />\n兩個後生仔 chur就唔怕chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腳力體力都完全沒問題（好似係）<br />\n係驚列車班次就唔到導致計劃唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再次JJ插地核求各位高人指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45ed84889ae70f7b237f1e92a28c81ef1b6c03","tid":362243,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T19:29:37.000Z","msg":"沿途有咩餐廳係食過好食可唔可以share埋比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時鎖定秋田烏冬同仙台牛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a849b4da0bb05443be91081cf29d5c5b5a8a942","tid":362243,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沿途有咩餐廳係食過好食可唔可以share埋比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時鎖定秋田烏冬同仙台牛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵食用TEBELOG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebb17ef94dbdfaf2cc247516c978c45a2dbe563","tid":362243,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沿途有咩餐廳係食過好食可唔可以share埋比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時鎖定秋田烏冬同仙台牛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵食用TEBELOG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90267ee58366ce8be232dc111704fa40418c26b0","tid":362243,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f932271e6b4e4c4be2c13878acbf323bc73354","tid":362243,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"青森古川市場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/blogs/%E6%9C%89%E5%86%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%86%B1-%E9%9D%92%E6%A3%AE%E5%BF%85%E9%A3%9F%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%A0%8C%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%B0%E7%80%89%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E9%A3%AF-x-%E7%89%B9%E8%A3%BD%E5%8D%83%E5%B1%A4%E5%91%B3%E5%99%8C%E8%B1%AC%E6%89%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg